{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be modern and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Forge Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e52121;\n            --secondary-color: #f08080;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --footer-background: #2c2c2c;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, #a01515 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .games-container {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #2c2c2c;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(229,33,33,0.4);\n        }\n\n        .game-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content {\n            padding: 25px;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-content h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 40px auto 0;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #3a3a3a;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 40px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #a01515;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: #aaa;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        .fade-in {\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(20px);\n            transition: opacity 0.8s ease-out, transform 0.8s ease-out;\n        }\n\n        .fade-in.visible {\n            opacity: 1;\n            transform: translateY(0);\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive Design */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n\n            .section h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            .games-container {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n\n            .contact-form input,\n            .contact-form textarea {\n                padding: 12px;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n\n            .cta-button {\n                padding: 12px 25px;\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Crimson Forge Studios</h1>\n        <p>Crafting worlds, forging legends. Experience the next evolution in gaming.</p>\n        <a href=\"#games\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Games</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"games\" class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Featured Games</h2>\n        <div class=\"games-container\">\n            <div class=\"game-card fade-in\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/e52121/ffffff?text=Game+1\" alt=\"Game 1 Screenshot\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Nova Odyssey</h3>\n                    <p>Embark on an epic spacefaring adventure across a vast, procedurally generated galaxy. Discover new worlds, battle alien threats, and forge your own destiny.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card fade-in\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/e52121/ffffff?text=Game+2\" alt=\"Game 2 Screenshot\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Shadow's Embrace</h3>\n                    <p>A dark fantasy action RPG where you delve into ancient ruins, master forbidden magic, and confront terrifying creatures in a world shrouded in eternal night.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card fade-in\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/e52121/ffffff?text=Game+3\" alt=\"Game 3 Screenshot\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Project Chimera</h3>\n                    <p>Unleash your inner beast in this fast-paced multiplayer shooter. Customize your hybrid creature and dominate the arena in intense tactical combat.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: #2c2c2c;\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content fade-in\">\n            <h3>The Forge</h3>\n            <p>Crimson Forge Studios is a passionate team of game developers dedicated to creating unforgettable interactive experiences. Founded in 2020, our mission is to push the boundaries of storytelling, gameplay, and visual artistry. We believe in innovation, collaboration, and the power of games to inspire, entertain, and connect people.</p>\n            <p>From sweeping open worlds to intense competitive arenas, we pour our heart and soul into every project, striving to deliver games that players will love and remember for years to come.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-form fade-in\">\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Forge Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.classList.add('visible');\n                    }\n                });\n            }, { threshold: 0.1 });\n\n            document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach(element => {\n                observer.observe(element);\n            });\n\n            const contactForm = document.getElementById('contactForm');\n            contactForm.addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n                event.preventDefault();\n                alert('Message sent! Thank you for reaching out.');\n                contactForm.reset();\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}